Package net.proteusframework.cms

General CMS classes.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Negotiable
    Represents negotiation logic for a rendered PageElement.
    PageElement
    Represents an element in a page.
    PageElementModel<PE extends PageElement>
    Represents a Component in CMS.
    PageElementModelFactory<PE extends PageElement>
    Provider of ICMSComponents.
    Secured
    Represents security information for a rendered PageElement.
    Trashable
    Implementors of this interface can be put in the "Trash".
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractPageElementModelFactory<PE extends PageElement>
    Default implementation of an PageElementModelFactory.
    BasePageElementModelFactory<PE extends PageElement>
    Component provider implementation that only returns the base component.
    CmsHostname
    Represents a Site hostname.
    CmsSite
    Represents a site.
    NDEList
    NDE list.
    NegotiableImpl
    Default negotiable implementation.
    PageElementModelImpl<PE extends PageElement>
    Default Component implementation.
    PageElementModelImpl.StandardIdentifier
    Utility for generating PageElementModel identifiers.
    PageElementPath
    Represents a path for a PageElement.
    PageElementPathDisassembled
    Utility class for querying page element paths without loading the entities.
    SecuredImpl
    Implementation of Secured.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    FileSystemDirectory
    A set of predefined directories.
  • Exception Summary
